\mathbb{R},\mathcal{T}
\mathcal{T} = \{]-a,a[ \mid a > 0\} \cup \{\emptyset,\mathbb{R}\}
\mathcal{T}
\cup_{n \in \mathbb{N}} ]-2 + \frac{1}{n} , 2 -\frac{1}{n}[ = [-2,2]
